To insert a time signature change in the arrange window right click on the space right below the grid display (image below)

[[File:Ableton Live time signature change.png]]



Then type in the time signature you want in the display that appears.


[[File:Ableton Live time signature display.png]]


You can also right click the flag and edit, rename or delete the time signature.


[[File:Ableton Live time signature menu.png]]



